  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently, lighthouse uses `--testnet <testnet>` to choose between medalla, spadina, \"others\".\r\n\r\nCome main net, it would be useful to have a `--network <network>` parameter that can take main as well as medalla and other supported test networks.\r\n\r\nRationale: Makes life easier with docker-compose. The same entrypoint or command structure can be used for main and testnet, just the name of the network changes. Needing to choose between `--testnet <testnet>` and \"something else\" for mainnet is cumbersome via `.env`\r\n",
